  "title": "WAITER SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Duties</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Delivering excellent customer service</li>\n  <li>Ensure smooth operations to achieve good customer satisfaction</li>\n  <li>Taking orders, serving of beverages to customers</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and housekeeping of work areas.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>At least 2 years relavant working experience</li>\n  <li>Able to work on Weekends and PH</li>\n  <li>Able to work in fast-pace environment.</li>\n  <li>Able to stand long time.</li>\n  <li>Able to do everything when manpower is not enough. Including clean, stock and supply designated facility areas (dusting, sweeping, vacuuming, mopping)</li>\n  <li>Extensive food and beverage (F&amp;B) knowledge, with ability to remember and recall ingredients and dishes to inform customers and wait staff</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with restaurant management software/ POS</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership, motivational and people skills</li>\n</ol>",
